title: Anahanta - Island of Love Audiostrobe CD [MP3]
description:
Audiostrobe CD for those of you with Audiostrobe compatible Light and Sound Machines. 

I'd like to invite you to a mental walk to a place associated with only positive memories. Tranquil and relaxing music but also vivid and powerful sounds are meant to help you create personal pictures in which you can move freely and recover. With every song the mind will become free for new thoughts and ideas and all tension will dissolve.

Includes 2 versions:

Single Track: Continuous light show
Multiple Tracks: Lights fade in at beginning of each track and fade out at end of each track.
